metadata.name: Sweetest Chicks
metadata.description:
This is a sweet message from the most adorable chicks, every time you have a hard time, please look at this message.

"Fuck it all, just do it, move on and shine!"

Tools traditional art:
Paper A3 (30 cm x 40 cm)
Graphite Pencils (2B, 4B, 8B)
Mechanical Eraser
Brush
Paper Stump

The result of traditional art was combined with manual digital art on procreate.

3000 x 4237 px
